events.name: Indiana Pacers at Los Angeles Lakers

headlines.description: — As Commissioner Adam Silver prepared to hand LeBron James the MVP trophy of the inaugural NBA In-Season Tournament, he cautioned that “it doesn't come with a franchise.”
headlines.shortLinkText: Anthony Davis leads Lakers to NBA In-Season Tournament title, 123-109 over Pacers
